      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "2018 — call #1\n\nJust rejected OpenAI offer\nto go to FAIR.\n\nIlya called, very angry.\n\"Why didn't you even discuss\nit before rejecting?\"\n\"Is the money not enough?\"\n\nSaining: vague answers. Hangs up.",
