      "text": "July 2024 — call #2\n\nSSI just founded.\nEmail: come work together.\n\nTopic: how to give AI\nthe ability to love.\n\nSaining asks: what about\nmultimodality?\n\nIlya: \"already solved\nwell enough.\"\n\nSaining declines.",
